\c 18 Hezekia mambo waJudha 1 Zvino negore rechitatu raHoshea mwanakomana waEra ma- mbo weIsiraeri, Hezekia mwanakornana waAhazi mambo waJudha wakatanga ushe. 2 Akatanga kubata ushe ava nama- kore ana makumi maviri namashanu; akabata ushe paJerusaremu makore ma- kumi maviri namapfumbamwe; zita ra- mai vake rakanga riri Abhi mukunda waZekariya. 3 Akaita zvakarurama pa- mberi paJehovha, sezvakaita baba vake Dhavhidhi. 4 Akabvisa matunhu akakwi- rira, akaputsa shongwe, akaparadza ma- tanda okunamata nawo; akaputsa-putsa nyoka yendarira yakanga yakaitwa na- Mosesi; nokuti kusvikira pamazuva iwayo vana veIsiraeri vaiipisira zvino- nhuwira, akaitumidza Nehushitani. 5 Aka- tenda kuna Jehovha Mwari weIsiraeri; naizvozvo hakuna wakanga akafanana naye pakati pamadzimarnbo ose aJudha, kuna vakamutevera, kana vakamutangira. 6 Nokuti wakanamatira Jehovha, haana kutsauka pakumutevera, asi wakache- ngeta mirairo yake, yakarairwa Mosesi naJehovha. 7 Jehovha akava naye; kwose kwaakaenda wakafambiswa zvakanaka;
